<http://scilake-project.eu/res/bbf33015#offset_35137_35502>
        a                         nif:OffsetBasedString , <dfki:ScientificDocumentPart> ;
        nif:anchorOf              "The third strategy we propose is related to the power that art in general, and music in particular, have to promote awareness over a specific issue, in the case of the third strategy, environmental awareness. Fostering awareness is useful in promoting a public discussion, eventually leading to individual behavioral and habitual changes or even policy development." ;
